OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDisabled man 'stunned      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcouncil took back savings' 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A man with a life-limiting condition   
OL,6, has said he is "stunned" his local     
OL,7, authority "clawed back" money he saved 
OL,8, to go on holiday with his carers.      
OL,10,FBy skipping cinema trips approved for  
OL,11,Fhis wellbeing by the council, Nathan   
OL,12,FLee Davies saved up money from his     
OL,13,Fround-the-clock care fund.             
OL,15,FHe wanted a six-day break in Florida to
OL,16,F"have a bit of respite from the mundane
OL,17,Freality of everyday life".             
OL,19,FWrexham County Borough Council said:   
OL,20,F"Surplus funds are to be returned."    
